snippet.title: Raster Blaster for Apple II
snippet.description: A simple pinball game for the Apple II I played as a kid.  Note: Something wonky about the emulation this time, so it goes ludicrous speed every so often and you can't really win at pinball when that happens, so I use a very cheap tactic :p
